                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <div class="white-trans-bg diagonal-bottom">
                            <div class="section-head">
                                <img src="/images/terms-trendingTopics-header-lg.jpg" alt="New Business">
                                <h2>Trending Topics</h2>
                            </div>
                            <p>This is where you can keep up with the hot news of the day in veterinary care. We’ll showcase topics that opinion makers in your business are discussing right now, so you can make it part of your social media conversation.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <div class="white-trans-bg diagonal-bottom">
                            <div class="section-head">
                                <img src="/images/terms-socialTips-header-lg.jpg" alt="New Business">
